Cac don vi: px, %
Mac dinh: tren xuong duoi, trai qua phai
+ Alignment:
	+ block: 
		+ can trai => mac dinh => margin-right: auto
		+ can phai: margin-left: auto
		+ can giua
	+ inline: 
		+ xep tren 1 hang => giong nhu text
		+ text-align: cho thanh phan cha

+ Dat dang hien thi: display:
+ Block, inline, inline-block:

+ Block: 
	+ co the dat chieu rong, chieu cao cho no
+ Inline element:
	+ Khong the dat chieu rong chieu cao
	+ Dc doi xu nhu text:
		+ chieu cao: font-size
	+ Chieu rong bang noi dung ben trong
+ inline-block:
	+ Giong inline
 	+ xep tren 1 hang
 	+ dat duoc chieu rong, chieu cao

+ Border:
	+ Viet tat: [rong] [kieu border] [mau vien]
	+ border-width:
	+ border-style:
	+ border-color:

	border-top: [rong] [kieu border] [mau vien]
+ max-width:
+ max-height:

===========================
Flex:
+ Su dung flex:
	+ Dat thuoc tinh display cho cha: display: flex;
	+ Sap xep 1 thanh phan con => theo 1 truc (main) ngang
	+ flex-direction:
		- xac dinh truc chinh theo huong nao
		+ column: cot => truc main => tren xuong duoi
		+ row-reverse
		+ column-reverse;
	+ justify-content:
		+ cach sap xep cac thanh phan con => theo 1 truc (main)
		+ flex-start: xep o dau truc
		+ flex-end: xep o cuoi truc
		+ center: xep o giua
		+ space-between: co khoang cach o giua 
		+ space-around: co khoang cach xung quanh 
	+ align-items:
		+ sap xep cac thanh phan con cross

	+ flex-wrap: bao boc
		+ Xuong hang hay khong

+ Cac thanh phan con:
	+ flex-grow: [1 con so]
		+ Ti le chia phan thua con lai trong tp cha
		+ Theo chieu truc main
		grow: thua => lon len => cho du => theo ti le
		shrink: thieu => nho lai => cho du => theo ti le
	+ flex-shrink: 1 con so
	+ flex-basis: Kich thuoc theo truc main;
		+ Chinh la width khi truc main nam ngang 
		+ Chinh la height khi truc main nam doc
	+ order
	
